==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: yuck
<hw>yuck</hw>, <pos>interj.</pos> <def>an interjection expressing
repugnance or distaste.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>yuck</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: yuck
<hw>yuck</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a laugh; also, a joke or gag; --
usually used in the plural, <as>as, the skit got lots of
<ex>yucks</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> laugh; gag; joke</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yuckel</ent>⟦br⟧
